# Implementation Plan: HomelinkGlobal Real Estate Prototype

This plan outlines the steps to build and run the `homelinkglobal-prototype` Next.js application, integrating pre-existing source files with newly created utility modules, a premium filter panel, public assets, and project configurations.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The prototype will be configured with **Next.js 15** and **Tailwind CSS v4** (using PostCSS integration), matching the `@import "tailwindcss";` present in `src/app/globals.css`.
>
> We will also generate 3 high-quality property images using the AI image generation tool to populate the public assets folder.

## Proposed Changes

We will introduce the project root configuration files, add utility helpers, create a premium `FiltersPanel` component, and generate mock property images.

