## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Install dependencies (`npm install`).
- Build the Next.js application (`npm run build`) to verify there are no TypeScript compile-time errors or missing assets.

### Manual Verification
- Spin up the local development server (`npm run dev`).
- Run a browser agent to verify that the home page, search bar, filters page, details page, and inquiries form work correctly and look premium.
